{
  "slug": "mex问题",
  "title": "MEX问题",
  "type": "知识点",
  "tags": [],
  "difficulty": null,
  "summary": "",
  "link": "",
  "link_text": "",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": "经典问题",
  "format": "markdown",
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "html": "<strong>“加数容易删数难，求值容易求和难。”</strong>",
      "depth": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "html": "<strong>“求值看定义，求和搞贡献。”</strong>",
      "depth": 1
    },
    {
      "heading": "性质",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>前缀性</strong>：$\\text{MEX} > k \\iff \\{0, 1, \\dots, k\\} \\subseteq \\text{Set}$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>间隙性</strong>：$\\text{MEX} = k \\iff k \\notin \\text{Set} \\text{ 且 } k \\text{ 是满足此条件的最小值}$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>排他性</strong>：如果一个数 $v$ 在某个范围内缺失，那么这个范围的 MEX <strong>最大</strong>只能是 $v$。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "模型",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>单调增长模型</strong>：如果集合只进不出，MEX 具有<strong>单调不减性</strong>，用指针和 $vis$ 数组维护即可。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>动态/滑动模型</strong>：如果集合有进有出（如滑动窗口、区间查询）。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>权值线段树</strong>：维护每个数最后一次出现的位置，查找“最后一次出现位置 < $L$”的最小数。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>间隙分析</strong>：不看集合里有什么，看某个数 $v$ 在哪里缺失。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "一般来说，动态模型都<strong>不好维护</strong>，<strong>加数容易删数难</strong>，动态模型应先考虑<strong>问题转化</strong>或<strong>维护对象的转换</strong>。",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "求和问题考虑<strong>贡献法</strong>",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>思维转换公式</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$\\sum MEX(\\alpha) = \\sum_{k \\ge 1} \\text{Count}(MEX(\\alpha) \\ge k)$$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>为什么要这么转？</strong>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "直接求 $MEX(\\alpha)=k$ 需要满足两个条件：$0 \\dots k-1$ <strong>都在</strong>，且 $k$ <strong>不在</strong>。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "求 $MEX(\\alpha)\\ge k$ 只需要满足一个条件：$0 \\dots k-1$ <strong>都在</strong>。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>少考虑一个条件，逻辑复杂度降低一个量级。</strong>在树上，这代表你只需要维护一个包含 $\\{0 \\dots k-1\\}$ 的“最小连通块/链”，而不需要管 $k$ 在哪。",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
